OL,5, Italy's far-right leader Giorgia Meloni
OL,6, and her coalition allies have met      
OL,7, President Sergio Mattarella and say    
OL,8, they are ready to form a government "as
OL,9, quickly as possible".                  
OL,11,FHe is set to ask Ms Meloni in the      
OL,12,Fcoming hours to become prime minister. 
OL,14,FVeteran ex-Prime Minister Silvio       
OL,15,FBerlusconi attended the brief talks,   
OL,16,Fdespite shaking the coalition's unity  
OL,17,Fwith leaked pro-Putin remarks.         
OL,19,FMs Meloni has sought to assure Italy's 
OL,20,FWestern allies nothing will change.    
